# AT400 GNSS Antenna for RTK

## 1. Application

GNSS positioning technology has the advantages of all-weather, high precision, global coverage, high degree of automation, and strong real-time service capability.

The antenna is widely used in various fields, including continuous operation reference stations, deformation monitoring, earthquake monitoring, autonomous driving, driver training and examination, geodetic surveying, precision agriculture and marine measurement; it can also be selected for military applications according to application conditions.
